<item>
            <title>[SEC-2570] LogoutConfigurer supports GET by default when CSRF is enabled</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SEC-2570</link>
                <project id="10040" key="SEC">Spring Security</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Since commit 5082a046 for &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.spring.io/browse/SEC-2311&quot; title=&quot;LogoutConfigurer should by default allow other methods if CSRF is disabled&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SEC-2311&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SEC-2311&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, the default LogoutRequestMatcher supports all HTTP methods regardless of the CSRF configuration.&lt;/p&gt;

